OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFine start, with brighter or
OL,6,Fsunny spells. Cloud then gradually
OL,7,Fthickening from the west, with
OL,8,Foccasional showers possible, mainly in
OL,9,Fthe far west. These gradually
OL,10,Fspreading further east into the
OL,11,Fevening, but with some eastern and
OL,12,Fsoutheastern parts staying dry.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FCloudy with showers becoming
OL,15,Fwidespread through the evening, and
OL,16,Flikely merging into more persistent
OL,17,Fand occasionally heavy rain. Rain only
OL,18,Ferratically clearing east after dawn,
OL,19,Fbut with further showers following.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
