OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FEarly cloud will break with
OL,6,Fsome brighter or sunny spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping, but also scattered
OL,8,Fshowers. These turning heavy in
OL,9,Fplaces, with thunder and hail possible.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FFine
OL,12,Fand breezy Wednesday, before rain
OL,13,Fspreads east later. Breezy Thursday
OL,14,Fwith sunny spells and scattered
OL,15,Fshowers, heavy and thundery. Perhaps
OL,16,Fdrier Friday, but with further showers
OL,17,Flikely. Staying cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
